intrebare?: From the perspective of digital marketing, is SEO sufficient?
raspuns1: In most cases, SEO is sufficient, but placing dofollow links in anchor text, that redirects to popular websites improves a website page authority (PA).
raspuns2: Yes, SEO contains all the tools needed to drive new customers to a webpage.
raspuns3: No. Along SEO, using invisible keywords and duplicated content are needed for ranking higher in a SERP.
raspuns4: No, paid advertising, social media marketing, email marketing and content marketing complements SEO in bringing customers to a website.
raspuns corect: No, paid advertising, social media marketing, email marketing and content marketing complements SEO in bringing customers to a website.
